<plot>Fred Robbins, one of America's top-rated disc jockeys in the forties and fifties, throws some of his radio "platter chatter" between selections performed by Ray Anthony and Orchestra. Band vocalist Johnny Desmond sings "I'll Close My Eyes" and Dee Keating does "Lets Go Back and Kiss the Boys Again." The band finale is "Finiculi, Finiculi." Columbia production number 8958.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?606204</url></doc>
